⚡ Energy Trading Analytics Dashboard
Overview

This project presents an end-to-end analytics solution for electricity market trading using hourly European day-ahead market data.

The objective is to analyze trading strategy performance, market conditions, risk exposure, and price behavior through a complete data pipeline and interactive Power BI dashboard.

The project combines:

Market price analysis
Trading strategy evaluation
Risk management metrics
Market regime detection
Weather impact analysis
Project Structure
