Data Sources
Market Data

Hourly electricity market prices including:

Day-ahead electricity price
Position signals
Price volatility
Negative price events
Price spikes

Resolution:

Hourly data
Full year analysis
Weather Data

Integrated weather variables:

Temperature
Humidity
Wind speed
Rain

Used to investigate relationships between weather conditions and electricity prices.

Data Model

The Power BI model follows a star-schema approach.

Fact Tables
Fact_Market

Contains hourly market observations:

Datetime
Price
Position
Volatility
Negative price indicators
Weather variables
Fact_Trades

Contains executed trades:

Entry time
Exit time
Entry price
Exit price
PnL
Holding period
Fact_Risk

Contains risk analytics:

Daily PnL
Cumulative PnL
Drawdown
Rolling volatility
VaR metrics
Dimension Tables
Dim_Date

Calendar dimension used for time intelligence.

Dim_Strategy

Strategy metadata and identification.

Dashboard Pages
1. Executive Overview

Provides a high-level view of strategy performance:

Total PnL
Trade count
Average trade performance
Equity curve
Electricity price evolution
Monthly performance
2. Trading Activity & Exposure

Analyzes trading behavior:

Number of trades
Market exposure
Long vs flat time
Holding duration
Trade history
Best and worst trades
3. Risk Dashboard

Focuses on risk management:

Sharpe ratio
Value at Risk (VaR)
Maximum drawdown
Rolling volatility
Drawdown profile
Daily PnL distribution
4. Market Intelligence

Examines market conditions:

Electricity price evolution
Negative price events
Temperature impact
Wind speed impact
Market regime classification

Market regimes include:

Normal Market
High Volatility
Price Spike
Negative Price
Key Findings

The analysis identified:

The strategy achieved positive cumulative performance.
Market exposure was limited compared to total available hours.
Negative price events represented a significant market condition.
The strategy was active during a portion of negative price periods.
Risk metrics provide visibility into drawdowns and volatility behavior.
